import { Fragment, useState } from "react" import Head from "next/head" import Link from "next/link" import Header from "../header" import Footer from "../footer" import { toast, ToastContainer } from 'react-nextjs-toast' import axios from "axios" export default function Registartion() { const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(false) const [otpSent, setOtpSent] = useState(false) const [verifyingOtp, setVerifyingOtp] = useState(false) const onSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault() let name = e.target.name.value let email = e.target.email.value let password = e.target.password.value let confirmPassword = e.target.confirmPassword.value let phone = e.target.phone.value if (confirmPassword !== password) { toast.notify("Password and confirm password does not match!", { type: "error", title: "Error!" }) return false } setIsLoading(true) axios.post(`${process.env.API_URL}customer/registartion`, { name: name, email: email, password: password, phone: phone }).then((response) => { toast.notify("An OTP sent at your email address!", { type: "success", title: "OTP Sent!" }) setOtpSent(true) }).catch(err => { setIsLoading(false) }) } return ( Registartion - Gandhi
